This dark wooden staff is carved in the shape of a majestic stallion. While holding this staff, you can cast the [[phantom steed]] spell from it using your own power. Gain an additional [[stress]] box that you can only use to cast this spell. In addition, gain +1 [[impact]] when you [[push yourself]] to sprint.